data.title: 5 Triunfante 44-53
data.meta_description: 5 Triunfante 44-53 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document summarizes a research study that mapped the cultural properties and assets of Polangui, Albay, Philippines in order to identify and record its tangible and intangible cultural heritage. The study utilized cultural mapping and profiling frameworks to document local cultural resources. It revealed that Polangui has several valuable cultural assets related to its history, aesthetics, social practices, and spiritual values. The study recommends integrating this cultural profile into future development plans and using GIS mapping to visualize Polangui's cultural heritage assets, in order to enhance cultural pride and conservation.
